Various Categories:


Relational (SQL)----MySQL,SQLite, PostgreSQL
NoSQL(can be relational or otherwise)
     |____Key/value databases(Redis, MemcacheDB, riak)
     |____column based(cassandra, HBase)
     |____Document based(MongoDB, couchDB)
     |____Graph Based (OrientDB, Neo4j)
 
